      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:6:123:5",
      "text": [
        " سَمِعْتُ أَبَا الْحَسَنِ ( عليه السلام ) يَقُولُ الدُّبَّاءُ يَزِيدُ فِي الْعَقْلِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "From him, from Ali Bin Hassan, from Musa Bin Bakr who said, ",
          "‘I heard Abu Al-Hassan<sup>asws</sup> saying: ‘The gourd increases the intellect’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. It is narrated from the narrator of the previous Hadith from Ali ibn Hassan from Musa ibn Bakr who has said the following: “I once heard abu al-Hassan, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, saying, ‘Squash, gourd increases power of reason.’” "
        ]
      }
